DAY-4[04/05/2023]
1.Please ensure that, all the Classroom K8S Concepts covered so far, have to be practiced well both Technically and Theoretically as well for Interviews perspective like:
* Pods / Containers
* Jobs / CronJobs
* ReplicaSets
* Deployment
* Service / Headless Service
* Volumes / Persistent Volumes / Persistent Volume Claims
* Stateful Sets and
* Namespaces etc.




